snippet.textDisplay: Many gems of singing talent in Pakistan. I wish they would be wearing more comfortable clothing (than a suit) and have a comfortable seating for such a soothing song. Though Rahat-sir and didn't let that bother his performance. Not sure where the girl is from - she seemed nervous but delivered. I am surprised by no use of the Tabla in this composition which is beautiful but wonder if that wd be better. Thanks  for keeping this respectable music culture alive.- Respect from India
